data.description: Welcome to your charming 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home in Bennet, Colorado, built in 2021. This well-kept residence features a modern interior with an open floor plan connecting the living, dining, and kitchen areas. Upstairs, you'll find four spacious bedrooms, including a luxurious primary suite with an en-suite bathroom. Conveniently located, the home boasts a playground across the street, perfect for outdoor enjoyment. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a beautiful home in a tranquil suburban setting close to Denver's amenities and Colorado's natural beauty. Schedule your showing today!
